{"tid":2294124,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"23歲公務員 月入15,000元 每月能投資2,000元 想5年儲到150萬","createTime":"2020-11-20T18:54:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-21T09:56:39.000Z","uid":4007,"like":6,"dislike":162,"uniUserReply":67,"replies":[{"pid":"3f6ee95713e3bddf731288e5e8df650f7e4064bd","tid":2294124,"uid":4007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-20T18:54:52.000Z","msg":"讀者：龔成老師，你好！我今年23歲，任職公務員，月入15,000，現有32萬 現金，目標5年內儲到150萬。<br />\n撰文：經一編輯部｜圖片：新傳媒資料室<br />\n<br />\n請問資金上可如何分配及投資？<br />\n<br />\n另外，打算開始每月2000元買股票，該選哪一隻股票？<br />\n<br />\n謝謝！<br />\n<br />\n龔成老師 分析<br />\n如果要5年累積到$150萬，你要加強儲蓄，以及投資方面要進取少少，先做到。<br />\n<br />\n第一，每月要逼自己儲$8000-$10000，你可以想方法增加收入及控制支出，第二，要利用投資去進行增值。<br />\n<br />\n你可以要集中投資潛力股，但這就會較高風險，同時要求你有較高的投資實力。<br />\n<br />\n現金$32萬，你可以將一半投資股票，餘下一半就等機會。慢慢分注入，唔好急。<br />\n<br />\n你可以投資「平穩增值股」+「潛力股」，不過，由於潛力股要求你有一定的投資知識，因此這刻不用急著投資，你可以集中在平穩增值股先，潛力股小注好了。<br />\n<br />\n你可以考慮盈富（2800）、銀娛（0027）、恒基（0012）、港鐵（0066）、平安（2318）、粵海（0270）、領展（0823）、希慎（0014）、太古地產（1972）等，你可以了解下這些股票，然後從中選股。<br />\n<br />\n如果想增長力高少少，可考慮：華夏恆生科技ETF（3088）、阿里（9988）、騰訊（0700）、港交所（0388）、舜宇光學（2382）、小米（1810）、比亞迪（1211）、中生製藥（1177），但就要明白波動性比上述會高左，同時風險大左，你要自己平衡。<br />\n<br />\n現時大市處合理區，可以一邊投資一邊留現金，而餘下現金的運用，就是等大跌市時出手，如果你能在這段時間學好選股等技巧，到大跌市時就能把握機會，財富增值會更明顯。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.edigest.hk/article/207370/%e6%8a%95%e8%b3%87/23%e6%ad%b2-%e5%85%ac%e5%8b%99%e5%93%a1-%e6%9c%88%e5%85%a515000%e5%85%83-%e6%af%8f%e6%9c%88%e6%8a%95%e8%b3%87-2000%e5%85%83-5%e5%b9%b4-150%e8%90%ac/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.edigest.hk%2Farticle%2F207370%2F%25e6%258a%2595%25e8%25b3%2587%2F23%25e6%25ad%25b2-%25e5%2585%25ac%25e5%258b%2599%25e5%2593%25a1-%25e6%259c%2588%25e5%2585%25a515000%25e5%2585%2583-%25e6%25af%258f%25e6%259c%2588%25e6%258a%2595%25e8%25b3%2587-2000%25e5%2585%2583-5%25e5%25b9%25b4-150%25e8%2590%25ac%2F&d=HaoFMq3H8OfxnxI562yM34m5R6Uo%2BMV3ZOx7awwfaZg%3D&h=4b6aff73\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.edigest.hk/article/207370/%e6%8a%95%e8%b3%87/23%e6%ad%b2-%e5%85%ac%e5%8b%99%e5%93%a1-%e6%9c%88%e5%85%a515000%e5%85%83-%e6%af%8f%e6%9c%88%e6%8a%95%e8%b3%87-2000%e5%85%83-5%e5%b9%b4-150%e8%90%ac/</a>"},{"pid":"7c05ef4ebc8b4ef2f0f630c085499b39222e1f48","tid":2294124,"uid":227271,"like":119,"dislike":1,"score":118,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-20T18:56:26.000Z","msg":"問問題個人係咪玩野<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5ad6637df57283b068a9a78e9341e8fdcc2de61","tid":2294124,"uid":35658,"like":16,"dislike":31,"score":-15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-20T18:57:17.000Z","msg":"2800 3088<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n公務員<br />\n過多幾年會唔會比中共派人直接代替<br />\n<br />\n32萬進修下搵出路好過"},{"pid":"028eb1016a00e7509aec1139a9d01aebea3d1f7b","tid":2294124,"uid":131368,"like":28,"dislike":2,"score":26,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-20T18:58:50.000Z","msg":"All in Xpev nio佢下年就有1m"},{"pid":"66a0203fa2de177ecd78343b306be632a4e3ad97","tid":2294124,"uid":280640,"like":32,"dislike":1,"score":31,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-20T19:00:42.000Z","msg":"月供港股 越供越窮 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66c076a9f0aec257c4132563f738b45d09ed47b4","tid":2294124,"uid":89182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-20T19:06:54.000Z","msg":"1211 9988 700 1810 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6bd87799541ac0bbf626c76d5dc5529c632525dc","tid":2294124,"uid":49016,"like":189,"dislike":2,"score":187,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-